*******************************************************************************
showoriginal (M)	restores the first 2D spectrum in a 3D DOSY experiment
*******************************************************************************
NAME
	showoriginal (M)
SYNOPSIS
	showoriginal

DESCRIPTION 
	Restores the first 2D spectrum in a 3D DOSY experiment after it
has been saved by the dosy macro.

OPTIONS

FILES
	curexp+'/subexp/original2d'

SEE ALSO
	dosy
	makeslice

